WEBVTT

1
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:38.868
-[ThunderRumbling]
-[Baby Crying]

2
00:00:50.149 --> 00:00:52.617
-[Woman #1]Isitagirl?
-[Woman #2] Yes.

3
00:00:52.685 --> 00:00:54.414
[Woman #1]
Showmeitsarm.

4
00:00:54.486 --> 00:00:57.387
- [Woman #2]Shebears themark.
- [Woman #3]No!

5
00:00:57.456 --> 00:00:59.947
-[Sobbing]
-[Baby Crying]

6
00:01:00.025 --> 00:01:03.552
The omen is true.
I must tell my mother.

7
00:01:05.965 --> 00:01:08.092
- [ Sobbing ] Help me!
- [Woman #2]Ican't.

8
00:01:08.167 --> 00:01:10.965
- They're going to kill her.
- [Baby's Cries Continue]

9
00:01:18.878 --> 00:01:23.406
[Mother. Sobbing]
Oh. thankyou. Ethna. Thankyou.

10
00:01:31.924 --> 00:01:34.484
[Guard]
Standaside forQueen Bavmorda!

11
00:01:43.102 --> 00:01:45.229
[Barking. Snarling]

12
00:01:58.851 --> 00:02:01.342
You cannot
stop the prophecy!

13
00:02:01.420 --> 00:02:04.355
This child will have no power over me.
Start the ritual.

14
00:02:04.423 --> 00:02:09.292
- No. No!
- Where's the baby?

15
00:02:09.361 --> 00:02:11.795
The midwife.
Find that baby. Sorsha.

16
00:02:11.864 --> 00:02:15.231
Use the dogs.
Bring her back to me alive!

17
00:02:15.301 --> 00:02:17.428
Your reign ofterror
is at an end!

18
00:02:17.503 --> 00:02:19.596
She will come back.
and she will finish you!

19
00:02:19.672 --> 00:02:23.265
- [Guard]Silence. wench.
- Mybaby will finishyou!
- Kill her.

20
00:03:29.131 --> 00:03:33.534
[Barking. Howling]

21
00:03:41.811 --> 00:03:46.180
[Barks. Howls Continue]

22
00:04:01.497 --> 00:04:05.331
[ Gasping. Panting ]

23
00:04:06.035 --> 00:04:09.493
[DogBellowing]

24
00:04:09.572 --> 00:04:11.563
[ Baby Cying ]

25
00:04:16.112 --> 00:04:21.379
[Barking Continues]

26
00:05:18.274 --> 00:05:20.265
[ Cooing ]

27
00:05:33.372 --> 00:05:35.840
[Bird Twittering]

28
00:05:39.445 --> 00:05:41.379
[ Coos ]

29
00:05:50.456 --> 00:05:52.447
Dada! Dada!

30
00:05:55.861 --> 00:05:59.160
-Dada!Dada!
- Whoa! Whoa!

31
00:06:00.432 --> 00:06:03.663
Dada! Dada!
We found something in the river.

32
00:06:03.736 --> 00:06:05.670
I can't run offand play
with you now. Ranon.

33
00:06:05.738 --> 00:06:08.036
- I've got work to do.
- You gotta come. Hury!

34
00:06:09.541 --> 00:06:11.532
[ Chuckles ]

35
00:06:13.012 --> 00:06:15.572
Come on.

36
00:06:17.916 --> 00:06:20.942
Don't go near it.
We don't know where it's been.

37
00:06:21.020 --> 00:06:23.955
But. Dada. it's a baby.

38
00:06:24.023 --> 00:06:28.824
- It's not like us.
- No. It's not a Nelwyn.

39
00:06:28.894 --> 00:06:32.455
- Itlooks likea Daikinibaby.
- What's a Daikini?

40
00:06:32.531 --> 00:06:34.863
Daikinis are big.

41
00:06:34.933 --> 00:06:38.061
- Giants who live far away.
- [ Laughing ]

42
00:06:38.137 --> 00:06:40.435
Oh. she's so cute.

43
00:06:40.506 --> 00:06:44.533
- Can't we keep it. Dada?
- No!

44
00:06:44.610 --> 00:06:49.843
We'll push it downstream and forget
we ever saw it. Come on.

45
00:06:49.915 --> 00:06:51.849
- Come on.
- Ufgood! WillowUfgood!

46
00:06:51.917 --> 00:06:56.081
Shhh! It's the prefect.
That's all I need.

47
00:06:56.155 --> 00:06:59.613
Keep it quiet.
Don't touch it.

48
00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:04.994
[Woman]Mr. Burglekutt. myhusband
hasn'tstolenanything!

49
00:07:05.064 --> 00:07:07.055
Baaa!

50
00:07:10.469 --> 00:07:13.961
Ufgood. you still haven't
paid your debts to me.

51
00:07:14.039 --> 00:07:16.064
Where did you
get these seeds?

52
00:07:16.141 --> 00:07:18.871
Well. maybe I used magic.

53
00:07:18.944 --> 00:07:22.903
[ Laughs ] You're no sorcerer. Ufgood.
You're a clown.

54
00:07:22.981 --> 00:07:26.542
I sell the planting seeds around here.
Now tell me whereyou got them.

55
00:07:26.618 --> 00:07:30.076
My family's been gathering them
in the forest since last fall.

56
00:07:30.155 --> 00:07:33.181
- There's no law against that.
- [Children Laughing]

57
00:07:33.258 --> 00:07:38.423
Willow. you didn't leave
them alone by the river?

58
00:07:38.497 --> 00:07:40.829
Magic?
You'll need magic...

59
00:07:40.899 --> 00:07:43.265
ifyou expect to getyour planting
done before the rains start.

60
00:07:45.304 --> 00:07:50.833
I will have this land. And you're
gonna end up working in the mines.

61
00:07:53.045 --> 00:07:56.776
- [ Burglekutt ] Baaa--
- [ Hog Snorting ]

62
00:07:59.918 --> 00:08:02.910
[ Giggling ]
Oh. you're lovely.

63
00:08:02.988 --> 00:08:04.979
- Yes. you are.
- [ Coos ]

64
00:08:05.057 --> 00:08:09.494
- Kiaya!
- Oh. Willow!

65
00:08:09.561 --> 00:08:14.498
- Good girl. Good girl.
- Under no condition whatsoever...

66
00:08:14.566 --> 00:08:17.296
is anyone in this family
to fall in love with that baby.

67
00:08:17.369 --> 00:08:22.102
Yes. you are. Come on. Mims.
Come on. Come on.

68
00:08:22.174 --> 00:08:24.233
There we are. Come on.

69
00:08:24.309 --> 00:08:26.937
Hey. I will not be ignored!

70
00:08:27.012 --> 00:08:30.709
Mims? Ranon?

71
00:08:41.693 --> 00:08:43.854
- [ Fussing ]
- You'regonnabeall clean.

72
00:08:47.533 --> 00:08:50.434
[ Baby Giggling ]

73
00:08:50.502 --> 00:08:53.801
Willow. doyou thinkwe should
take her to the village council?

74
00:08:53.872 --> 00:08:56.466
No. No.
They'll think it's a bad omen.

75
00:08:56.542 --> 00:08:59.375
There'll be a flood or a drought.
and eveyone will blame me for it.

76
00:08:59.444 --> 00:09:02.345
""Willow Ufgood brought around
that Daikini. didn't he?

77
00:09:02.414 --> 00:09:05.440
That's right. He's that
lousy farmertoo. Let'sgethim!''

78
00:09:05.517 --> 00:09:09.578
- Willow. calm down.
- Calm down?

79
00:09:09.655 --> 00:09:11.714
Kiaya. tomorrow's my big day.

80
00:09:11.790 --> 00:09:15.521
Love. the HighAldwin hasn't
pickedanewapprenticeinyears.

81
00:09:15.594 --> 00:09:18.893
Tomorrow's gonna be different.
I just know he's gonna pick me.

82
00:09:21.633 --> 00:09:25.296
- Here. Hold her.
- Hey. no. I don't want her. Kiaya.

83
00:09:25.370 --> 00:09:28.168
- Hold herwhile I get some milk.
- Oh. no. no. Oh.

84
00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:32.973
- [ Giggling ]
- [ Squeals ]

85
00:09:35.814 --> 00:09:39.272
- Dada. she likes you.
- [ Giggles ]

86
00:09:41.053 --> 00:09:46.218
[ Cooing. Laughing ]

87
00:09:46.291 --> 00:09:47.459
-[RoosterCrowing]
- Bye.

88
00:09:47.459 --> 00:09:50.553
-[RoosterCrowing]
- Bye.

89
00:09:50.629 --> 00:09:54.531
- Come on. kids. Let's go.
- [ Mims Giggling ]

90
00:09:58.237 --> 00:10:00.501
-  [ Festive ]
- [ villagers Chattering ]

91
00:10:00.572 --> 00:10:04.167
[Willow]
I willnowmagicallyjoin therings!

92
00:10:05.677 --> 00:10:08.510
[Continues]

93
00:10:26.131 --> 00:10:28.759
- Whoa-ah!
- [ Laughing ]

94
00:10:33.538 --> 00:10:35.938
Thankyou. son.

95
00:10:36.008 --> 00:10:41.036
Ifyou're easily shocked.
please turn away.

96
00:10:41.113 --> 00:10:43.172
- [ Gasps ]
- [ Oohing And Aahing ]

97
00:10:44.983 --> 00:10:47.747
[Continues]

98
00:10:54.226 --> 00:10:56.160
[ Honking ]

99
00:10:56.228 --> 00:10:58.492
Give me a ripe one. Good.

100
00:11:04.703 --> 00:11:09.197
- [ Squeals ]
- And now. for my final amazing feat.

101
00:11:09.274 --> 00:11:14.109
- I will make this entire pig disappear!
- [ Skeptical Groans ]

102
00:11:14.179 --> 00:11:16.647
[ Laughs ]

103
00:11:18.951 --> 00:11:22.114
[ Squealing ]

104
00:11:22.187 --> 00:11:27.318
- Mims. see?
- Please. watch vey closely.

105
00:11:27.392 --> 00:11:33.024
- Wuppitybairn. deru. deru!
- [ Surprised Laughter]

106
00:11:35.267 --> 00:11:37.667
- Well--
- What happened toyour pig?

107
00:11:37.736 --> 00:11:40.296
- [PigSquealing]
- [ Gasps ]

108
00:11:40.372 --> 00:11:43.432
No!
Hey. come here. you!

109
00:11:47.879 --> 00:11:51.280
I seen enough.
[ Laughing ]

110
00:11:53.251 --> 00:11:56.880
[Fanfare]

111
00:12:00.892 --> 00:12:03.884
-[Low. Deep Horn Blows]
-[Villagers Chattering]

112
00:12:06.398 --> 00:12:09.663
Attention!
The High Aldwin...

113
00:12:09.735 --> 00:12:12.670
-willnowmakehis choice
forhisnewapprentice!
- You'll be all right.

114
00:12:12.738 --> 00:12:16.196
Bring forth the hopefuls.

115
00:12:16.274 --> 00:12:18.674
- Good luck.
- Good luck. Dada.

116
00:12:18.744 --> 00:12:22.510
Willow Ufgood. a hopeful?
How did he get picked?

117
00:12:22.581 --> 00:12:25.072
Is this ajoke?
[ Guffaws ]

118
00:12:25.150 --> 00:12:29.610
-[Burglekutt's Laughing Continues]
- Willow?

119
00:12:32.042 --> 00:12:37.480
Magic is the bloodstream
ofthe universe!

120
00:12:37.547 --> 00:12:42.109
Forget all you know...
or thinkyou know.

121
00:12:42.185 --> 00:12:46.212
All thatyour require
is your intuition.

122
00:12:46.290 --> 00:12:50.386
Now. the power
to control the world...

123
00:12:50.460 --> 00:12:54.954
is in which finger?

124
00:13:36.940 --> 00:13:41.468
- No apprentice this year!
- [ Onlookers Groan ]

125
00:13:41.545 --> 00:13:46.448
[Resumes]

126
00:13:53.924 --> 00:13:56.916
[Creature Bellowing]

127
00:13:58.095 --> 00:14:01.792
- [ Panicked Screams ]
-[Dog Barks]

128
00:14:01.865 --> 00:14:05.266
- Where's Mims?
- Idon'tknow. She was righthere!

129
00:14:05.335 --> 00:14:08.236
Take Ranon in there. quick!

130
00:14:08.305 --> 00:14:10.569
[ Growling ]

131
00:14:12.209 --> 00:14:14.439
[ Cying ]

132
00:14:16.146 --> 00:14:19.081
- Mims!
- [ Snarling ]

133
00:14:20.450 --> 00:14:22.611
- Mims!
- [ Screaming ]

134
00:14:22.686 --> 00:14:27.123
- [ Cying ]
- [ Snarling ]

135
00:14:28.558 --> 00:14:30.788
- [ Gasps ]
- [ Cying ]

136
00:14:30.861 --> 00:14:35.696
- Mims!
- Dada--

137
00:14:36.967 --> 00:14:40.027
- I'm scared. Dada!
- [ Baby Cying ]

138
00:14:46.743 --> 00:14:50.235
[Ferocious Growling]

139
00:14:50.313 --> 00:14:52.907
Come on!

140
00:14:52.983 --> 00:14:55.315
- [ Dog Snarling ]
- [ Yelling ]

141
00:15:10.567 --> 00:15:13.536
- vohnkar!
- [ Growls ]

142
00:15:13.603 --> 00:15:17.232
- [ Dog Whimpers ]
- [ Men Grunting ]

143
00:15:23.046 --> 00:15:25.947
- Check to make sure.
- It's dead!

144
00:15:28.285 --> 00:15:30.082
Dada! Dada!

145
00:15:33.423 --> 00:15:35.687
It was looking
for somebody's baby!

146
00:15:35.759 --> 00:15:38.626
[ Baby Cying ]

147
00:15:38.695 --> 00:15:42.529
- Mommy.
- Kiaya!

148
00:15:49.906 --> 00:15:53.239
Kiaya!
Kiaya!

149
00:15:53.310 --> 00:15:56.336
- [ Baby Coos ]
- I'm here.

150
00:15:56.413 --> 00:15:58.381
[ Relieved Sigh ]

151
00:16:00.417 --> 00:16:04.046
- Oh. Kiaya.
- [ Baby Fussing ]

152
00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:06.315
We can't keep
the baby. Kiaya.

153
00:16:06.389 --> 00:16:09.256
We have to take her
to the village council.

154
00:16:13.330 --> 00:16:16.026
[People Chattering]

155
00:16:22.739 --> 00:16:27.642
Silence! One beast we can kill.
but there may be more.

156
00:16:27.711 --> 00:16:30.111
Andyoucanbeassured
that they won'tgive up...

157
00:16:30.180 --> 00:16:32.148
until they findwhat
they're looking for!

158
00:16:32.215 --> 00:16:35.480
-[Man #1]It'sasign!
-[Man #2] Who's toblame forthis?

159
00:16:35.552 --> 00:16:38.043
[Man #3] Wemustfindthe culprit
andthrowhim in thepit!

160
00:16:38.121 --> 00:16:43.252
- [ Shouting In Agreement ]
- [Villagers]In thepit!In thepit!

161
00:16:43.326 --> 00:16:45.453
In thepit!In thepit!

162
00:16:45.529 --> 00:16:48.828
-In thepit!In thepit!
- Willow.

163
00:16:48.899 --> 00:16:53.268
-[Chanting Continues]
- WillowUfgood.

164
00:16:53.336 --> 00:16:55.804
Come forward.

165
00:16:55.872 --> 00:16:59.865
[ villagers Murmuring ]

166
00:17:01.444 --> 00:17:06.780
My children found this baby
alone by the river. High Aldwin.

167
00:17:08.218 --> 00:17:12.314
[ Cying ]

168
00:17:12.389 --> 00:17:14.550
- A Daikini child.
- [ villagers Gasping ]

169
00:17:14.624 --> 00:17:17.855
That's what the beasts want.
Let's give it back to them!

170
00:17:17.928 --> 00:17:19.020
[ villagers ]
Yeah!

171
00:17:19.095 --> 00:17:22.394
- They'll kill her! You can't!
- It isn't one ofus.

172
00:17:22.465 --> 00:17:25.127
This child is special!

173
00:17:25.201 --> 00:17:29.501
This child must be taken beyond
the boundaries ofourvillage.

174
00:17:29.573 --> 00:17:32.633
All the way across
the great river...

175
00:17:32.709 --> 00:17:34.802
to the Daikini crossroads.

176
00:17:34.878 --> 00:17:39.577
- Well. who'll do that?
- Itseems only fair...

177
00:17:39.649 --> 00:17:43.016
that the man to take
this baby to the crossroads...

178
00:17:43.086 --> 00:17:46.055
be the vey man who
plucked it out ofthe river.

179
00:17:47.624 --> 00:17:50.252
- I nominate Willow Ufgood.
- [ villagers Shout Agreement ]

180
00:17:50.327 --> 00:17:52.852
No!

181
00:17:52.929 --> 00:17:56.490
I will consult the bones!

182
00:17:57.500 --> 00:17:58.933
[ Fussing ]

183
00:18:03.873 --> 00:18:09.368
- The bones tell me... nothing.
-[Baby Coos]

184
00:18:11.014 --> 00:18:14.950
Doyou have any love
for this child?

185
00:18:23.360 --> 00:18:27.854
Yes. Yes. I do.

186
00:18:27.931 --> 00:18:32.334
- The bones have spoken!
- [ villagers Murmuring ]

187
00:18:32.402 --> 00:18:36.361
Willow Ufgood. the safety
ofthis village depends upon you.

188
00:18:36.439 --> 00:18:40.535
- Praise the bones!
- [ Repeating ] Praise the bones!

189
00:18:40.610 --> 00:18:43.101
[HighAldwin]
Butyou willneedhelp.

190
00:18:43.179 --> 00:18:48.549
Whohas the courage toprotect
ourbrave fellowonhisjourney?

191
00:18:50.587 --> 00:18:54.683
- I'll go with him.
- Ah. Meegosh.

192
00:18:54.758 --> 00:18:58.057
- Bxcellent choice.
- I'll go!

193
00:18:58.128 --> 00:19:00.596
[ villagers. Shouting ]
vohnkar! vohnkar!

194
00:19:00.664 --> 00:19:03.360
No! Not vohnkar!
He's the best warrior in the village!

195
00:19:03.433 --> 00:19:06.630
Weneedhim here!
Vohnkar. stepback!

196
00:19:14.644 --> 00:19:17.238
All this expedition needs
is a leader.

197
00:19:17.313 --> 00:19:20.680
Andaccording to thebones...

198
00:19:20.750 --> 00:19:24.151
- Bh--
-thatleaderis...

199
00:19:24.220 --> 00:19:25.652
you. Burglekutt!

200
00:19:25.652 --> 00:19:26.641
you. Burglekutt!

201
00:19:26.720 --> 00:19:30.212
vohnkar!

202
00:19:30.290 --> 00:19:34.386
- What's your problem. son?
- How doyou mean?

203
00:19:34.461 --> 00:19:39.763
When I held up my fingers
what was your first impulse?

204
00:19:39.833 --> 00:19:43.735
- Well. it was stupid.
-Just tell me.

205
00:19:43.804 --> 00:19:48.264
- To pick my own finger.
- Aha! That was the correct answer.

206
00:19:48.342 --> 00:19:53.075
You lack faith in yourself.
More than anyone in the village.

207
00:19:53.147 --> 00:19:55.775
you have the potential
to be a great sorcerer.

208
00:19:55.849 --> 00:20:00.684
Now. when you're out there.
listen toyour own heart.

209
00:20:02.623 --> 00:20:07.651
- These will protectyou. They're magic!
- Acorns?

210
00:20:07.728 --> 00:20:11.755
Anything you throw them at
turns to stone.

211
00:20:14.802 --> 00:20:18.033
You have much to learn.
young Ufgood.

212
00:20:30.984 --> 00:20:35.444
- Areyou scared. Dada?
- No!

213
00:20:35.522 --> 00:20:39.754
Bven with fairies in the woods that'll
putyou to sleep for a hundred years?

214
00:20:41.762 --> 00:20:43.889
- Doesn't bother me.
- Brownies?

215
00:20:43.964 --> 00:20:46.899
- Dragons?
- Trolls?

216
00:20:46.967 --> 00:20:50.403
Trolls that'll skin you alive
and takeyour face off?

217
00:20:50.471 --> 00:20:54.100
Ranon!
You know I hate trolls.

218
00:20:54.174 --> 00:20:57.302
I can beyour guard
and caryyour spear.

219
00:20:57.377 --> 00:20:58.935
Me too. Me too. Dada.

220
00:21:00.547 --> 00:21:05.883
What a lucky father I am. I wish
I could takeyou bobbins with me.

221
00:21:08.956 --> 00:21:11.516
Good-bye. Dada.

222
00:21:13.560 --> 00:21:17.553
Go play!
Go on.

223
00:21:21.535 --> 00:21:25.062
We've never been apart.

224
00:21:26.106 --> 00:21:29.439
I miss you already.

225
00:21:30.777 --> 00:21:34.213
Don't wory. Kiaya.
I'll be fine.

226
00:21:34.281 --> 00:21:36.215
I'll be back
beforeyou know it.

227
00:21:38.452 --> 00:21:41.182
Well. remember
to keep herwarm.

228
00:21:43.223 --> 00:21:45.953
And... here.

229
00:21:48.095 --> 00:21:50.893
This will bring you luck.

230
00:22:04.077 --> 00:22:06.409
Good brave people!

231
00:22:08.248 --> 00:22:10.978
The outerworld is
no place for a Nelwyn.

232
00:22:11.051 --> 00:22:15.784
Give the baby to the first
Daikini you see. then hury home.

233
00:22:19.293 --> 00:22:22.888
Tuatha...
lokwathrak... tuatha!

234
00:22:22.963 --> 00:22:26.490
[HighAldwin]
Goin the direction thebirdis flying!

235
00:22:26.567 --> 00:22:30.503
- [ Giggling ]
- Ooh.

236
00:22:30.571 --> 00:22:33.404
It's going back to the village!

237
00:22:35.242 --> 00:22:37.233
Ignore the bird.
Follow the river.

238
00:22:37.311 --> 00:22:39.541
Move out!

239
00:23:00.500 --> 00:23:03.435
[ Fussing ]

240
00:23:03.503 --> 00:23:06.961
- Hold on. Meegosh.
- What's wrong?

241
00:23:07.040 --> 00:23:11.067
- We have to stop.
- Stop? Why?

242
00:23:11.144 --> 00:23:13.612
- The baby's sick.
- [ Bawling ]

243
00:23:17.584 --> 00:23:22.180
She's not sick!
Let me see.

244
00:23:22.256 --> 00:23:25.453
Uhaghh!
Take her! Take her!

245
00:23:25.525 --> 00:23:27.993
-[Burglekutt's Groans Continue]
- [ Laughing ]

246
00:23:28.061 --> 00:23:31.121
She'll be fine
once she gets some rest.

247
00:23:31.198 --> 00:23:33.393
[ Cooing ]

248
00:23:33.467 --> 00:23:35.162
[ Groaning ]
Clean me up.

249
00:23:38.805 --> 00:23:42.036
[ Bavmorda ] I didn't askyou
to bring me a dead nursemaid.

250
00:23:42.109 --> 00:23:46.011
-Sorsha. you're useless!
-I'm backtracking the nursemaid's trail.

251
00:23:46.079 --> 00:23:48.274
I'll find where
she hid the baby.

252
00:23:50.250 --> 00:23:52.514
Ah. General Kael. at last.

253
00:23:52.586 --> 00:23:57.319
My queen. I have destroyed
the castle at Galladoorn.

254
00:23:57.391 --> 00:24:01.088
Well done. But now I have
another task foryou.

255
00:24:01.161 --> 00:24:06.622
Help my daughter to find
that tiny. helpless baby...

256
00:24:06.700 --> 00:24:08.691
that continues
somehow to elude her.

257
00:24:10.604 --> 00:24:12.572
The baby ofthe prophecy?

258
00:24:12.639 --> 00:24:16.075
- The one that would destroyyou?
- I need that baby alive.

259
00:24:16.143 --> 00:24:18.611
Imustperform
theritualthat will...

260
00:24:18.679 --> 00:24:22.046
exile the child's spirit
into oblivion.

261
00:24:22.115 --> 00:24:24.845
- Find her!
- I don't need his help. Mother.

262
00:24:24.918 --> 00:24:26.977
You'll do as I say. child.

263
00:24:33.427 --> 00:24:35.588
I read the signs.

264
00:24:35.662 --> 00:24:38.859
One day. I fear. your daughter
will betrayyou.

265
00:24:38.932 --> 00:24:43.096
I trust her loyalty
more than I trustyours.

266
00:24:48.041 --> 00:24:53.843
[ Baby Cooing ]

267
00:24:53.914 --> 00:24:55.905
- [ Squealing ]
-[Dogs Barking. MenShouting]

268
00:24:58.819 --> 00:25:01.379
- Move!
-[Baby Fussing]

269
00:25:01.455 --> 00:25:03.389
It's an ambush.
Come on. Move!

270
00:25:03.457 --> 00:25:07.621
-[Dogs Barking]
- [ Horses Neighing ]

271
00:25:07.694 --> 00:25:11.425
- Come on!
- [ Dogs Snarling ]

272
00:25:21.007 --> 00:25:23.942
The Nelwyns have got the baby.
We've searched the village.

273
00:25:24.010 --> 00:25:26.979
Butagroup ofthem
are on theroadsomewhere.

274
00:25:27.047 --> 00:25:28.878
Theycouldn'thavegone far!

275
00:25:28.949 --> 00:25:31.918
Widen the search
and report to Sorsha!

276
00:25:33.153 --> 00:25:36.919
- [Dog Barks Fading]
- [ Sputtering Sigh ]

277
00:25:39.326 --> 00:25:42.022
Come. We'll keep to the woods.

278
00:26:20.801 --> 00:26:24.999
That's it!
It's the crossroads!

279
00:26:27.007 --> 00:26:29.066
[Dogs Howling
In The Distance]

280
00:26:41.421 --> 00:26:44.364
[ vohnkar] Keep this fire high.
We don't know what's out there.

281
00:26:44.498 --> 00:26:47.524
[ Whimpers ]

282
00:26:49.903 --> 00:26:52.371
-[Creature Shrieking]
- What was that?

283
00:26:53.707 --> 00:26:56.505
Get the spears!

284
00:26:59.046 --> 00:27:02.038
[ Cying ]

285
00:27:07.921 --> 00:27:10.651
- [Shrieking]
- [ Gasps ]

286
00:27:12.960 --> 00:27:14.894
- [ Growling ]
- Uhh. Uhh.

287
00:27:14.962 --> 00:27:18.830
Give me some water. peck.
oryou die.

288
00:27:18.899 --> 00:27:21.333
Doyouunderstand?

289
00:27:21.401 --> 00:27:23.301
- Water.
- Yeah.

290
00:27:23.370 --> 00:27:25.361
[ Grunts. Groans ]

291
00:27:25.439 --> 00:27:27.430
Hury up!

292
00:27:31.445 --> 00:27:34.346
Get me some water.
you measly little pecks.

293
00:27:34.414 --> 00:27:37.872
It's a Daikini.
We're in luck.

294
00:27:37.951 --> 00:27:40.385
We can't give her to him!

295
00:27:40.454 --> 00:27:44.413
- Somebody put him there for a reason.
- We've got to get rid ofher.

296
00:27:44.491 --> 00:27:47.085
- Those soldiers are after us.
- Shhh.

297
00:27:47.161 --> 00:27:50.028
He's looking right at us.

298
00:27:53.967 --> 00:27:55.935
We've got to give
that baby to somebody.

299
00:27:56.003 --> 00:27:58.870
I'm somebody.

300
00:27:58.939 --> 00:28:03.308
Let me out ofhere. I'll take care
ofthe baby. [ Smooching Sounds ]

301
00:28:05.145 --> 00:28:09.741
- I trust him completely.
- But he tried to strangle me.

302
00:28:09.817 --> 00:28:13.753
- I want to go home!
- No. Burglekutt!

303
00:28:13.821 --> 00:28:17.188
- Weshould wait!
- Areyou challenging my authority?

304
00:28:17.257 --> 00:28:20.624
As far as this baby
is concerned... yes.

305
00:28:20.694 --> 00:28:23.720
Don'tlisten tohim. Burglekutt.

306
00:28:23.797 --> 00:28:28.894
Fine. You stay here alone.
but we're going.

307
00:28:28.969 --> 00:28:31.199
That'sabadidea.
Verybad.

308
00:28:31.271 --> 00:28:34.707
- Dangerous out there.
- [Burglekutt]Get thegear. men.

309
00:28:34.775 --> 00:28:38.336
- vohnkar--
- It's not his decision!

310
00:28:38.412 --> 00:28:42.348
Burglekutt. you're troll dung.

311
00:28:42.416 --> 00:28:44.077
Don't let him
talk toyou that way.

312
00:28:44.151 --> 00:28:46.244
Listen here. runt.

313
00:28:46.320 --> 00:28:50.313
Whileyou're wasting time here.
your fields aren't getting planted.

314
00:28:50.390 --> 00:28:54.690
- Think about it!
- Burglekutt. I'm gonna--

315
00:28:54.761 --> 00:28:58.128
You're gonna what?

316
00:28:58.198 --> 00:29:01.964
[ Laughs ]

317
00:29:02.035 --> 00:29:04.595
Some day. Burglekutt.
Some day.

318
00:29:04.671 --> 00:29:06.696
vohnkar. let's go!

319
00:29:10.377 --> 00:29:13.073
Meegosh. areyou coming?

320
00:29:15.349 --> 00:29:18.944
- I'm staying.
- [ Laughs ] Come on. men.

321
00:29:19.019 --> 00:29:23.217
Burglekutt. let me out ofhere.
I'll take care ofthe baby. I swear.

322
00:29:23.290 --> 00:29:25.952
justletme outofhere.
Please!

323
00:29:26.026 --> 00:29:29.484
vohnkar. let me borrow that spear...
just for a minute.

324
00:29:29.563 --> 00:29:31.827
Get--
Well. at least get me some water!

325
00:29:31.899 --> 00:29:36.859
Burglekutt. don't leave me alone
with these two! [ Frustrated Grunt ]

326
00:29:36.937 --> 00:29:41.738
- [ Baby Cying ]
- What'll we do now. Willow?

327
00:29:41.808 --> 00:29:44.436
Well. that was really stupid. peck.

328
00:29:44.511 --> 00:29:49.312
- Don't call me a peck.
- Oh. I'm sory... peck.

329
00:29:49.383 --> 00:29:53.149
- Peck. peck. peck. peck.
- You be careful!

330
00:29:53.220 --> 00:29:56.986
I'm a powerful sorcerer.
See this acorn?

331
00:29:58.425 --> 00:30:02.919
- I'll throw it. and turn you to stone.
- Whoo--

332
00:30:02.996 --> 00:30:04.930
I'm really scared.

333
00:30:04.998 --> 00:30:07.865
No. don't!Don't!

334
00:30:07.935 --> 00:30:10.768
There's a peck here
with an acorn pointed at me!

335
00:30:10.837 --> 00:30:13.499
Oh. I wouldn't
want to waste it.

336
00:30:13.573 --> 00:30:16.838
Ha!
Peck. peck. peck. peck.

337
00:30:16.910 --> 00:30:19.470
peck. peck. peck.
peck. peck!

338
00:30:19.546 --> 00:30:21.844
[Insects Twittering]

339
00:30:45.138 --> 00:30:48.005
[ Neighing ]

340
00:30:48.075 --> 00:30:50.976
- [ Both Grunting ]
- [Meegosh] What was that?

341
00:30:54.348 --> 00:30:58.045
Mornin'. boys.

342
00:30:58.118 --> 00:31:02.248
Rough night last night.
wasn't it?

343
00:31:02.322 --> 00:31:05.689
I don't think I introduced
myselfyesterday.

344
00:31:05.759 --> 00:31:09.217
My name is Madmartigan.
and you are. uh--

345
00:31:09.296 --> 00:31:12.265
No. Meegosh.
Don't go near him.

346
00:31:12.332 --> 00:31:15.768
- He's dangerous.
- I am not.

347
00:31:15.836 --> 00:31:17.997
Good.

348
00:31:22.743 --> 00:31:25.041
Stop! Wait!

349
00:31:26.780 --> 00:31:29.544
- [Horse Neighing]
- Whoa!

350
00:31:29.616 --> 00:31:32.744
- [ Chuckles ]
- [Horse Gallops Past]

351
00:31:34.988 --> 00:31:39.516
- What's going on?
- Smells like a battle.

352
00:31:39.593 --> 00:31:42.118
I supposeyou're a warrior.

353
00:31:42.195 --> 00:31:44.686
I am the greatest swordsman
that ever lived.

354
00:31:44.765 --> 00:31:47.598
Hmph.

355
00:31:47.667 --> 00:31:51.433
Say. uh-- Could I have
some ofthat water?

356
00:31:52.439 --> 00:31:55.101
[ Sips Noisily]

357
00:31:57.477 --> 00:32:01.072
[ Sobbing ]

358
00:32:01.148 --> 00:32:05.915
I don't know why I ty.
[ Sobbing ]

359
00:32:10.690 --> 00:32:13.955
I guess I am gonna die here.
Who cares.

360
00:32:14.027 --> 00:32:15.961
- Here.
- Thanks. friend. Oh!

361
00:32:16.029 --> 00:32:18.429
- [DistantRumbling]
- What's that?

362
00:32:18.498 --> 00:32:22.457
[Madmartigan]I'dsay
two orthreehundredhorses.

363
00:32:22.536 --> 00:32:26.495
five or six wagons...
and about a thousand fools.

364
00:32:26.573 --> 00:32:29.167
[Madmartigan Grunting]

365
00:32:29.242 --> 00:32:33.008
- Thankyou. Ohh--
- Come on. Meegosh.

366
00:32:33.080 --> 00:32:35.776
[ Panting ]

367
00:32:37.350 --> 00:32:41.081
[ Willow ] It's gonna be
all right. little bobbin.

368
00:32:41.154 --> 00:32:43.645
[Drums Beating]

369
00:32:47.027 --> 00:32:50.963
- [ Fussing ]
- Bveything's gonna be all right.

370
00:32:51.031 --> 00:32:54.228
[Drumbeats Continue]

371
00:32:54.301 --> 00:32:57.395
- Bxcuse me. sir.
- Out ofthe way. peck!

372
00:32:59.339 --> 00:33:01.705
Uh. pardonme.

373
00:33:01.775 --> 00:33:03.868
Uh--

374
00:33:03.944 --> 00:33:09.439
[Drumbeats Continue]

375
00:33:09.516 --> 00:33:14.749
Bxcuse me. sir. We found one
ofyour babies in ourvillage.

376
00:33:14.821 --> 00:33:17.722
Will you please
take care ofher?

377
00:33:17.791 --> 00:33:22.228
We're going into battle. little ones.
Find a woman to take care ofher.

378
00:33:23.663 --> 00:33:26.826
They thoughtyou were
a woman. Airk.

379
00:33:26.900 --> 00:33:29.300
Well--
[ Laughs ]

380
00:33:29.369 --> 00:33:33.931
-Madmartigan. what did you do this time?
-Nothing you wouldn't have done.

381
00:33:34.007 --> 00:33:36.373
Ialwaysknew
you'dendup ina crow's cage.

382
00:33:36.443 --> 00:33:38.308
At least I'm not
down there herding sheep.

383
00:33:38.378 --> 00:33:39.868
What areyou doing this far north?

384
00:33:39.946 --> 00:33:41.971
The Nockmaar army
destroyed Galladoorn.

385
00:33:42.983 --> 00:33:44.280
The castle?

386
00:33:44.351 --> 00:33:46.819
Bavmorda's troops are
crushing eveything in sight.

387
00:33:46.887 --> 00:33:48.821
Come on.
Let me out ofhere. Airk.

388
00:33:48.889 --> 00:33:51.125
Give me a sword.
I'll win this war foryou.

389
00:33:51.259 --> 00:33:55.559
Madmartigan--
I still serve Galladoorn.

390
00:33:55.630 --> 00:33:57.621
Youserveno one.

391
00:33:57.699 --> 00:33:59.929
Remember?

392
00:34:00.001 --> 00:34:03.232
Sit in your coffin and rot.

393
00:34:03.304 --> 00:34:06.364
- Hyah!
- Wait. Airk. You need me!

394
00:34:06.441 --> 00:34:08.875
I'll be around
long afteryou're dead!

395
00:34:08.943 --> 00:34:11.571
When Igetoutofhere.
I'mgonna cutyourheadoff...

396
00:34:11.646 --> 00:34:13.739
and stick it
on a pig pole!

397
00:34:13.815 --> 00:34:15.840
[ Baby Cooing ]

398
00:34:31.266 --> 00:34:35.999
- [ Fussing ]
- I miss Kiaya and the bobbins.

399
00:34:39.974 --> 00:34:43.774
We're running out offood.

400
00:34:43.845 --> 00:34:47.474
Nobody's gonna
take care ofthat baby.

401
00:34:47.549 --> 00:34:50.518
You know why?
Nobody cares.

402
00:34:53.421 --> 00:34:56.948
Bxcept me.

403
00:34:57.025 --> 00:35:01.257
You want to go back toyour families.
I want out ofthis cage.

404
00:35:01.329 --> 00:35:05.288
Let me take care ofthat baby.
I'll look after her like she was my own.

405
00:35:05.366 --> 00:35:08.358
I believe he would. Willow.

406
00:35:08.436 --> 00:35:10.961
He doesn't know
anything about babies.

407
00:35:11.039 --> 00:35:16.272
Right. But I know
a lot ofwomen who do.

408
00:35:16.344 --> 00:35:19.279
IfIhadsomebodyin mylife.

409
00:35:19.347 --> 00:35:22.942
a little daughter. perhaps.

410
00:35:23.017 --> 00:35:26.282
I might have a reason
to go on living.

411
00:35:29.524 --> 00:35:32.322
You can't leave me
in here to die.

412
00:35:32.393 --> 00:35:35.453
Not when all I want
to do is protect her.

413
00:35:35.530 --> 00:35:38.363
[ Cooing ]

414
00:35:42.403 --> 00:35:45.099
[ Yells. Laughs ]

415
00:35:48.776 --> 00:35:52.678
I feel better!
[ Laughs ]

416
00:35:52.747 --> 00:35:56.478
-You've done the right thing! [ Whoops ]
-Okay. All right. All right.

417
00:35:56.551 --> 00:36:01.011
- You gotta promise to feed her.
- Come to Daddy. little darlin'.

418
00:36:01.089 --> 00:36:06.117
- And keep her clean.
- Absolutely.

419
00:36:06.194 --> 00:36:08.253
- [ Madmartigan ] Hee. hee. hee!
-[Baby Giggling]

420
00:36:08.329 --> 00:36:13.198
- Wheee!
- [ Baby Squeals ]

421
00:36:13.267 --> 00:36:16.532
She likes me.

422
00:36:16.604 --> 00:36:18.538
[ Giggles ]

423
00:36:18.606 --> 00:36:21.006
Here are her changing rags.

424
00:36:21.075 --> 00:36:23.270
- And her milk bladder.
- Any milk in there?

425
00:36:23.344 --> 00:36:27.610
- It's for her!
- I wouldn't steal from a baby.

426
00:36:29.350 --> 00:36:32.877
- [ Cooing ]
- You wory too much. peck.

427
00:36:32.954 --> 00:36:36.890
- It's Willow.
- I mean Willow.

428
00:36:36.958 --> 00:36:42.726
Now listen. boys-- Willow.
You've done the right thing.

429
00:36:42.797 --> 00:36:46.198
And I wantyou to get home
and bring your crop in.

430
00:36:52.707 --> 00:36:56.939
- Good-bye. little one.
-[Cooing]

431
00:37:05.653 --> 00:37:07.917
Please. take good care ofher.

432
00:37:09.691 --> 00:37:12.558
I giveyou myword ofhonor!

433
00:37:19.233 --> 00:37:23.135
- Meegosh. slow down!
- Oh. come on!

434
00:37:23.204 --> 00:37:27.436
Ifwe hury. we can be home by
tomorrow morning. We'll be heroes.

435
00:37:27.508 --> 00:37:31.035
- Doyou really think so?
- Sure.

436
00:37:31.112 --> 00:37:33.376
""Look. there's
Willow and Meegosh.

437
00:37:33.448 --> 00:37:35.678
The heroes have come home.''

438
00:37:35.750 --> 00:37:38.844
""Welcome back. boys.
You deserve medals!''

439
00:37:38.920 --> 00:37:43.152
- Yeah. Medals.
- [ Both Laughing ]

440
00:37:43.224 --> 00:37:46.955
Meegosh--

441
00:37:48.830 --> 00:37:52.960
- Did we do the right thing?
- Absolutely.

442
00:37:53.034 --> 00:37:57.334
- There's nothing to wory about.
- [Baby Crying]

443
00:38:00.341 --> 00:38:02.639
Hyah! Ha ha!

444
00:38:02.710 --> 00:38:07.943
Istole thebaby!Istole thebaby!
[Laughs]

445
00:38:08.015 --> 00:38:11.781
- Hyah!
- That's my baby!

446
00:38:11.853 --> 00:38:13.821
- Stop! Wait! Come back!
-[Baby Crying]

447
00:38:13.888 --> 00:38:17.051
Left. you stupid bird.
Left! Ha ha!

448
00:38:19.861 --> 00:38:23.126
- Ah!
- Ow!

449
00:38:23.197 --> 00:38:26.894
Brownies!
Let's get out ofhere!

450
00:38:26.968 --> 00:38:30.301
- Come on. Meegosh!
- Ow!

451
00:38:31.305 --> 00:38:35.036
- Uhh-uh-huh-uh.
- Uhh. Oww!

452
00:38:36.344 --> 00:38:38.403
We'll outrun 'em!

453
00:38:38.479 --> 00:38:41.346
- [ Both Yelling ]
-[Laughing]

454
00:38:43.151 --> 00:38:47.247
-Hey. ugly. wake up![Laughing]
- [ Gasps ]

455
00:38:47.321 --> 00:38:49.755
Huh?

456
00:38:49.824 --> 00:38:54.921
- [ Grunts. Groans ]
- Stand your ground. He's our prisoner.

457
00:38:54.996 --> 00:38:57.760
Meegosh.
where's the baby?

458
00:38:57.832 --> 00:38:59.766
[Woman's Voice]
Bring the Nelwyns tome.

459
00:38:59.834 --> 00:39:01.233
All right. you heard her!

460
00:39:01.302 --> 00:39:05.102
- What's going on?
- Shut up. or I'll breakyour nose.

461
00:39:05.173 --> 00:39:07.539
You are mine to toywith.

462
00:39:07.608 --> 00:39:11.135
Forward!

463
00:39:11.212 --> 00:39:15.012
- Gimme the rope.
- [ All Grunting ]

464
00:39:15.082 --> 00:39:19.109
Where--
Where...

465
00:39:19.187 --> 00:39:21.451
did you get that baby?

466
00:39:21.522 --> 00:39:26.255
I stole it from a stupid Daikini.
[ Laughs ]

467
00:39:26.427 --> 00:39:29.590
[Woman]
Franjean. release the Nelwyns.

468
00:39:29.664 --> 00:39:33.930
-Andstoppestering them.
- Uh-oh.

469
00:39:34.001 --> 00:39:36.094
Ahh--

470
00:39:36.170 --> 00:39:38.297
[ Muttering ]

471
00:39:38.372 --> 00:39:40.306
- [ Rope Pops ]
- Yaah!

472
00:39:40.374 --> 00:39:44.504
[ Grunting ]

473
00:39:44.579 --> 00:39:47.810
